OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of Sussex couple jailed in Iran
OL,4,Csay they have lost contact with them
OL,6,FThe "terrified" family of a Sussex
OL,7,Fcouple jailed for 10 years in Iran on
OL,8,Fspying charges say they have lost all
OL,9,Fcontact with them.
OL,11,FLindsay and Craig Foreman, both 53,
OL,12,Fwere arrested in January 2025 while
OL,13,Ftravelling through Iran during an
OL,14,Faround-the-world trip by motorcycle.
OL,16,FThe couple, from East Sussex, are
OL,17,Fbeing held in Tehran's Evin prison and
OL,18,Fsentenced on espionage charges, which
OL,19,Fthey deny.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
