FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of Sussex couple jailed in Iran
OL,4,Csay they have lost contact with them
OL,6,FTheir family fears the couple's
OL,7,Ftelephone access - their only means of
OL,8,Fcontact with the outside world - has
OL,9,Fbeen cut off as payback for speaking
OL,10,Fout about their detention.
OL,12,FLindsay's son, Joe Bennett, said: "We
OL,13,Fsimply do not know if my mum and Craig
OL,14,Fare safe.
OL,16,F"Craig told us that they might have to
OL,17,Fstop eating if their calls were taken
OL,18,Faway.
OL,20,F"I have not spoken to my mum for over
OL,21,Fa week now.
OL,26,@tD@cOUxD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of Sussex couple jailed in Iran
OL,4,Csay they have lost contact with them
OL,6,F"Every day of silence makes it worse.
OL,8,F"We don't know what is happening to
OL,9,Fthem and we are terrified for them."
OL,11,FTelephone access stopped earlier this
OL,12,Fmonth after they gave a media
OL,13,Finterview when they said they felt
OL,14,F"abandoned" while in detention and
OL,15,Ffelt that the channels to try and
OL,16,Fsecure their release were closing,
OL,17,Ftheir campaign group has said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@AOUqD@dO]vD@AOUvD@KO]
