OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of Sussex couple jailed in Iran
OL,4,Csay they have lost contact with them
OL,6,FIn February, the Foreign Office said
OL,7,Fit had "temporarily" withdrawn its
OL,8,Fstaff from Iran amid the threat of US
OL,9,Fstrikes against the country.
OL,11,FIt also advises against all travel to
OL,12,FIran warning that British and British-
OL,13,FIranian nationals face a "significant
OL,14,Frisk of arrest, questioning or
OL,15,Fdetention".
OL,17,FIt adds that "having a British
OL,18,Fpassport or connections to the UK can
OL,19,Fbe reason enough for the Iranian
OL,20,Fauthorities to detain you".
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@TO]uD@ZOUwD@JO]yD@NOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
