PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of Sussex couple jailed in Iran
OL,4,Csay they have lost contact with them
OL,6,FA spokesman previously described the
OL,7,Fjail sentences the pair received as
OL,8,F"completely appalling and totally
OL,9,Funjustifiable", saying their welfare
OL,10,Fis a "priority" for the government.
OL,12,FMs Foreman, in her first interview
OL,13,Fsince the US and Israel launched
OL,14,Fstrikes against Iran on February 28,
OL,15,Ftold ITV News she could hear the
OL,16,F"whistling noise of missiles and the
OL,17,Fhum of the drones" nearby and "people
OL,18,Fwere hyperventilating, screaming".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@NO]rD@FOUrD@OO]xD@AOUyD@RO]yD@
OL,26,A_OUzD@aO]
