PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of Sussex couple jailed in Iran
OL,4,Csay they have lost contact with them
OL,6,F"The first day you could feel it, the
OL,7,Fimpact of the bombs, the rockets, the
OL,8,Fmissiles."
OL,10,FTalking about prison conditions, Ms
OL,11,FForeman said: "When the buildings
OL,12,Fshake, there is nowhere to go.
OL,14,F"These buildings are not designed for
OL,15,Fsafety.
OL,17,F"There's no fire escape, there's no
OL,18,Faccess to the outside for us.
OL,20,F"If the building collapses, that will
OL,21,Fbe the end."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]sD@OOUvD@AOUyD@AOU|D@AOU}D@
OL,26,ALO]
